cu.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause the gNB to fail during initialization as the value is not one of the valid options (none, info, annoying).

du.explanation_en: Setting the absolute frequency SSB to a negative value of -1 will cause the gNB to fail during initialization as the frequency must be positive.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SSB 絕對頻率設定為負值 -1 會導致 gNB 在初始化期間失敗，因為頻率必須為正數。
